          "title": "Overview",
          "order": 1,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "heading",
              "text": "What is SEB Client?"
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "Safe Exam Browser (SEB) is a secure browser environment for taking online exams safely. It turns any computer into a secure workstation by controlling access to utilities and preventing students from using unauthorized resources."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
